item.title: CVE-2024-27291|2024-02-29T21:49:26.633Z -- jhpyle -- docassemble
item.description: Docassemble is an expert system for guided interviews and document assembly. Prior to 1.4.97, it is possible to create a URL that acts as an open redirect. The vulnerability has been patched in version 1.4.97 of the master branch.
